buri.ddmsence.ddms.summary

Class PostalAddress

  • Object
    • buri.ddmsence.AbstractBaseComponent
      • buri.ddmsence.ddms.summary.PostalAddress
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDDMSComponent

    public final class PostalAddress
extends AbstractBaseComponent
    An immutable implementation of ddms:postalAddress.

    In DDMS2.03.03.14.0.1/4.15.0

    History

    The custom definition of postal address was replaced by TSPI addresses in DDMS 5.0.
